-- Reckitt Benckiser to Stop Selling Suboxone Tablets
-- B y   M a t t h e w   B o y l e
-- 2012-09-25T07:13:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-25/reckitt-benckiser-to-stop-selling-suboxone-tablets.html
Reckitt Benckiser Group Plc (RB/)  will
cease production of the Suboxone opioid-dependency drug in
tablet form, a person familiar with the decision said today.  The person, who declined to be named, said an announcement
from the company will be made later today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Matthew Boyle in London at 
